snippet: The beauty queen and her sister were last seen getting into a car to go to a party on Thursday.
abstract: Police in Honduras say they are intensifying search for Maria Jose Alvarado, Miss Honduras beauty queen, who has been missing for almost a week along with her sister Sofia.
lead_paragraph: The beauty queen and her sister were last seen getting into a car to go to a party on Thursday.

headline.main: Miss Honduras Is Target of Search
headline.print_headline: Miss Honduras Is Target of Search
